     3	## TL;DR (For humans)
     4	**What you'll get:** A reusable skill that helps an agent design and generate clean conversational operations systems: reservation, lending, seat allocation, appointment booking, and similar workflows. It will include a working reference starter with chat UI, backend orchestration, domain examples, and verification scripts.
     5	
     6	**Why this approach:** The airline demo is useful because its core pattern is portable: shared context first, triage-only routing, specialist agents, handoffs, guardrails, and observable state updates. This plan generalizes that pattern instead of cloning airline-specific details.
     7	
     8	**What it will NOT do:** It will not connect to real production reservation systems, payment providers, or identity providers. It will not mutate real inventory. It will not become an airline-only demo.
